headline: Welltower Announces Date of First Quarter 2025 Earnings Release, Conference Call and Webcast
summary: Welltower® Inc. (NYSE: WELL) today announced it will release first quarter 2025 financial results after the close of trading on the New York Stock Exchange on Monday, April 28, 2025. The Company will host a conference call and webcast on Tuesday, April 29, 2025, at 9:00 a.m. ET to discuss these results. The Company's earnings release will be available in the Investor Relations section of the Company's website.
